prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon watercolor of a slightly frazzled but happy sloth wearing a tiny party hat, precariously balancing a teetering stack of colorful, clumsily wrapped birthday presents. The sloth is hanging upside down from a tree branch, smiling cheekily at the viewer. Below the sloth, in the center of the card, the text "happy belated-ish birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The style is a flat 2D watercolor painting with soft, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture background, and organic paint bleeds around the edges of the sloth and gifts.
